Mr.Swapnil Bangur i/b. Ashok Jain for Defendants in Suit Nos.1262, 1263, 1266 of 1990 and Suit No.3709/89. P.C. :- P.C. :- P.C. :- 1. Learned Advocate for the parties state that the parties have agreed to preliminary decree passed in terms of Minutes of Decree. Draft Minutes of Order taken on record and marked "X" for identification. Accordingly, there will be decree in terms of preliminary decree.
